name: RouteOfAdministrationOfTherapeuticAgents
title: Route of Administration of Therapeutic Agents
publisher: HL7 US Realm Program Management Steward
purpose:
(Clinical Focus: This set of values contain concepts that represent the physiological administration path of a therapeutic agent into or onto a patient.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this set of values is allow encoding of ordered or administered, medication routes.),(Inclusion Criteria: SNOMED CT: concept descendantOf ("284009009:Route of administration value ...")
SPL: Selected concepts that are descendent of C38114 as determined by the FDA. These concepts are linked to "SPL Drug Route of Administration Terminology (Code C54455)" by Concept_In_Subset.),(Exclusion Criteria: SNOMED CT - No excluded clause
SPL: As determined by the FDA those routes not to be used in SPL (navigational concepts, etc.))
